Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道  你以为我有多老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, course I do. How old d'you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候超级喜欢他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was massively into them as a kid.
