Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢那件衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was dead pleased with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很严肃  很有政治意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it was serious, political.
