Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要我穿那件衣服  我妈妈就会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But whenever I wore it my mum would go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"现在你能看到那些战斗机了吗  小内"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Can you see those fighter planes yet, Nev?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈们就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's mums for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想起这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What made you think of that?
