Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实没见过一架战斗机  所以也许...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never did see any fighter planes, so maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在也有那种感觉  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got that feeling now, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我就那种感觉  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, I do, guv.
