Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...如果这样不起作用  那...之后怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..if this doesn't work, then... what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他出现  我们就能抓到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When he does show up, we've got him.
