Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走进了拉维妮娅花园6号的私人车道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's entering the driveway of number six Lavinia Gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4号监控点  4号监控点  是否收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OP4. OP4. Did you receive?
