Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动组待命  随时准备行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Mobiles standing by and ready to deploy.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以看他怎么动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We could be watching him work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动手  我重复  不要动手  所有人待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Negative, I repeat, negative, all units are to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那是什么  手电筒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit. What's that, a torch?
