Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  如果伪装暴露  也就毁掉了整个行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, if we blow our cover, then we've blown the op.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一下  直到确定就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just wait till we're sure it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警报解除  警报解除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stand down, stand down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个年轻白人男性回家休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's a young white male going home to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他可真幸福  -6号监控点结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 'Lucky bastard.' - OP6 out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动组撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Mobiles standing down.'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累得我浑身僵硬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm stiff as a board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道他们怎么每晚坚持下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know how they do it night after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  他们白天会睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They sleep in the day, for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能晚点去上班吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't you go in later?
