Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前两场我都缺席  上面提醒我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I missed the last two and it's been suggested from above
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好关注这个方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I might want to start taking an interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-否则呢  -我不会让他们有借口抢走我的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Or what? - I'm not giving them any excuse to take my toys away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是在M25公路上身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you get killed on the M25,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是要去参加健康安全汇报会的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they'll be the ones who need Health and Safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特派代表着领导力强而有力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, delegation's a hallmark of strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-而不是软弱无能  -路易丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- not weak, leadership. - Louise..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是把自己往绝路上逼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're running yourself into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为内森不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cos Nathan's away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在你的工作和生活间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's possible to care about your job
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到...怎么说  平衡  还是有可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and find... I don't know, balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我不行  -你认真试过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not for me. - How hard have you looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这样的人  一旦投入  不计安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the way I am, in for a penny, in for a pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我羡慕那些能把工作就留在工作场所的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I envy people who can leave their work at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你才不羡慕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  过去这几周观察你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's watching you these last weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一直很压抑  紧张  殚精竭虑...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know it's been frustrating, nerve-wracking, exhausting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不太确定...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定...是只因为要抓住这个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just not sure... it's just about catching this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What d'you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你这么投入这个案子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you're going at it this hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你知道这是最后一次...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because you know it's the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...而这个事实让你前所未有的害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..and you're dreading that more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看看你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, just look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你整晚在外挨冻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're out all night in the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早还准备正常上班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and straight back in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不想错过  也不愿浪费时间睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't want to miss a thing, or waste time sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你知道退休后心里会有多空虚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cos you know how big a hole that's gonna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不怪你  我怎么会怪你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I don't blame you. How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你最熟悉的事情  你就是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're in your element, it's just who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望当这些都结束  当你退休...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just hope when it's over, when you're done...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现有的生活能令你满足  我能令你满足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that what we have is enough. That I'm enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也能满足于酒吧小游戏和花园中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you can make your peace with pub quizzes and garden centres.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前半句没问题  后半句不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes to the former, no to the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你又要拿这事取笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, go on, make a joke of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-除非被胁迫或者假装可以  -科林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Unless under duress or in disguise. - Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕接下来要发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am scared about what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道工作  说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The job's all I know and, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不敢想象退休后是什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't even imagine what it's gonna be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  我得走了  -但我们会没事  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right, I'd better go. - We'll be all right, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监控点随时会报告就位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Observation points will be radioing in any minute.
