Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.62,0:25:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们八点见  -嗯  回头见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll see you at eight. - 'Yeah. See you then.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.34,0:26:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和谁讲这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抓住他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.62,0:26:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把水烧上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll put the kettle on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-西蒙·摩根  -我是科林·萨顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 'Simon Morgan.' - It's Colin Sutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.90,0:26:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉这么早给你打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry to call you so early,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.14,0:26:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想亲自告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wanted you to hear it from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来我们抓住他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it looks like we've got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.74,0:26:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我还在  老天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Yeah, I'm still here. Fucking hell.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.62,0:26:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我也是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们位于拉维妮娅花园的一个监控点发现...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of our OPs on Lavinia Gardens saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.73,0:27:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'I'm on my way in.'
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.58,0:27:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  等你到了我把情况告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK, I'll fill you in when you get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.94,0:27:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位我们老大  萨顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the boss, Mr Sutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.22,0:27:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幸会啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.10,0:27:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要击球还是投球啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what are you, batting or bowling?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.14,0:27:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不太喜欢板球吧  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not into cricket, are you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喜欢啊  -但你还是不打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - But you still don't play?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.42,0:27:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我打  偶尔打  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do, as a matter of fact, yeah, occasionally. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打  我当然打了  击球和投球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, yes, of course I do. Bat and bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.53,0:27:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真不错啊  我的膝盖不允许我投球了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, good for you. My knees won't let me bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.22,0:27:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还能像以往一样地挥棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I can still swing a bat around as well as I ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.01,0:27:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, tell me, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得英格兰在南非的机会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what do you think of England's chances in South Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.14,0:28:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我们可以再加一名快投手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think we could do with one more fast bowler
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得我们有很大的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, er, I think we've got a great chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.34,0:28:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我一直也这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, man, that's what I've been saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.01,0:28:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  得告诉你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just so you're aware, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子患了多发性硬化症  我是她主要的护工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my wife suffers from MS and I'm her primary carer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.81,0:28:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显  这会让她受惊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Obviously, this'll come as a shock to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.22,0:28:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I imagine it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.70,0:28:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想确保她会受到照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I just want to make sure she's properly taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.74,0:28:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-否则我会很担心  -抱歉打断一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll be worried otherwise. - Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.77,0:28:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰特先生  请您签署一下DNA取样好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr Grant, could I have your signature for the DNA sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.65,0:28:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去录指纹吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Prints now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:29:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还用老式的方法呢  -对  还是湿定型好用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Still doing 'em old school? - Oh, yeah. Can't beat a wet set.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把右手给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need your right hand, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.38,0:29:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白你为什么要费这个劲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't know why you're bothering,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.29,0:29:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我总是戴着手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know I always wore gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.10,0:29:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚你说了句很有意思的话啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was an interesting comment you made just now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.77,0:29:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于总是戴着手套的那句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about always wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能取一个你的签名吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Er, could we get a signature off you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.30,0:29:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是确认你说了那句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just to confirm you made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.53,0:30:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚是否接触过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you had any contact
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.57,0:30:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何体弱或年长的人  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a vulnerable or an elderly person tonight, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.65,0:30:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一个屁股摔坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no-one out there with a broken hip
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.01,0:30:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法拿到电话的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who can't get to the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.25,0:30:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人需要帮助和注意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No-one in need of help and attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.33,0:30:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚没见任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't visited anyone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.61,0:30:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有什么不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very important that you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.81,0:30:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必问清楚  德尔罗伊  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if there's anything you don't understand, Delroy. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.37,0:30:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天呐  天呐  天呐  -怎么了  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, dear, oh, dear, oh, dear. - What is it, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好去调查一下我儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You really want to have a look at my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.65,0:30:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.81,0:30:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说很难...非常难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is hard for me... so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鉴于这些罪名的严重性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..but given the seriousness of the offences,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们能抓对人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to make sure you get the right man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的DNA会跟我的一样  或很类似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His DNA's gonna be the same as mine, or very similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.68,0:31:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外加我们身高一致  而且他住在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}plus we're the same height, and he lives in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么直到现在才告诉我  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did you wait until now to tell us this, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.40,0:31:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然处于受惊状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm still in a state of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.09,0:31:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-胡扯  -对  当然是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Bullshit. - Yeah, course it's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.01,0:31:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎的DNA一样  但父子不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Twins can share DNA, but not fathers and sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他说得对  仍然可能很相似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's right, though, they can be very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.29,0:31:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们需要查这个吗  -对  我们得打几个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We need to jump on this? - Yeah, we need to make some calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.37,0:31:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让帕特丽夏去查儿子  然后我们取样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get Patricia to look the son up and we can get a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.92,0:31:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  立刻去办  老大  -并告诉她我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. Will do, boss. - And tell her I want to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.33,0:31:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可没闲着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't hang about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.89,0:31:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们确定是他吗  -我想是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We're sure it's him? - Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.77,0:31:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-DNA会确认  -他在系统里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- The DNA will confirm. - Was he in the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.61,0:31:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道  我直接来了这里  恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}TBC - I came straight here. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.96,0:31:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大日子  你的案子破了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your day, your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.29,0:31:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只是帮忙跨过了终点线  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I just helped it over the finish line. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.33,0:31:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我去看看团队  -好  我也去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll go check on the team. - Yeah, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.29,0:31:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只想看看他的脸  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I just wanna see his face. - Sure, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  所以他在系统里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OK, was he in the system or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.16,0:32:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很复杂  -他没开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's complicated. - He's not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.09,0:32:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听完他们解释后我不得不去躺会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to go and have a lie down when they explained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-只有你这样  肯尼  -说吧  内森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's just you, Kenny. - Go on, Nath.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.49,0:32:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99年在布罗姆利有一起盗窃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a burglary, back in '99 in Bromley.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.20,0:32:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方警察通知了米恩斯泰德团队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Local police inform the Minstead team,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们认为不是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they don't think it's Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.13,0:32:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不符合标准吗  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Didn't fit the criteria? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.25,0:32:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以布罗姆利就自己调查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So Bromley go ahead and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.13,0:32:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者有一个邻居看到一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now a neighbour of the victim sees a car
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.85,0:33:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她觉得有些可疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that she thinks looks suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就上报了车牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she reports the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.16,0:33:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一查发现登记在德尔罗伊·格兰特名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They run a trace and it's registered to a Delroy Grant
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.16,0:33:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是森林山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at an address in Forest Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把他名字输入全国警察数据库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They put his name in the PNC.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.09,0:33:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发现有六个名字一样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It IDs six people of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.44,0:33:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个在哈克尼  有盗窃犯罪史  也登记了DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One in Hackney, had a burglary conviction. DNA on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.65,0:33:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那这份样本和我们的犯罪现场样本呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. And this sample was compared to our scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.37,0:33:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们通知我们说哈克尼的德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They informed us that Hackney Delroy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.29,0:33:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wasn't Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.53,0:33:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听着很简单  -对  只不过不知为何那份结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sounds straightforward. - Yeah, except somehow that result
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.53,0:33:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被登记到了森林山的德尔罗伊档案名下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}became assigned to Forest Hill Delroy's profile
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.49,0:33:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并在我们的系统里建档了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a nominal was created on our system.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的错误成了我们的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their mistake became our mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  而且还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. And it gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.05,0:33:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队里有个警员在去找森林山的德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A DC from our team went to visit Forest Hill Delroy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.09,0:33:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查他盗窃案当晚的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to check his movements on the night of the burglary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.33,0:33:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.89,0:33:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没在家  结果也没再继续跟进了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was out and it was never followed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.85,0:33:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就是我们抓的德尔罗伊吗  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And that's the Delroy we just nicked? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.09,0:34:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转到右侧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.49,0:34:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果采样了他的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If his DNA had been taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.65,0:34:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立马就能鉴定出他是米恩斯泰德犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he would have instantly been identified as Minstead Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.89,0:34:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.28,0:34:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那刻起  德尔罗伊·格兰特这个人就被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From that moment on, the name Delroy Grant was ruled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.45,0:34:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向左侧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.93,0:34:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也没在取样名单上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he wasn't on the swabbing list?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  因为之前因DNA错误被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, been formally eliminated by DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.32,0:34:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所以就算用DNA取样法你们也抓不住他  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- So you'd never have got him that way anyway? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.20,0:34:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2001年  德尔罗伊·格兰特这个名字又出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In 2001, the name Delroy Grant cropped up again
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时有人拨打热线  说他是嫌犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when someone called the hotline pushing him as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.89,0:34:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在《犯罪调查》节目播出后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was after one of those Crimewatch appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没有采取任何行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the action got binned
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.68,0:34:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犯罪数据库说他测了DNA  被排除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because HOLMES said he'd been cleared by DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.68,0:34:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.49,0:34:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后有多少受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How many victims since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.57,0:35:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小德尔罗伊·格兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Delroy Grant Jr?'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.65,0:35:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人跟你一起住这里吗  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does, er, anyone live here with you, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.61,0:35:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈和我哥  什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mum and my brother. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.32,0:35:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没惹麻烦  也没有人去世  不是这类事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not in any trouble. No-one's died, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.01,0:35:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们有些不太好开口的消息要告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we do have some difficult news to share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.53,0:35:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.97,0:35:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  能坐下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, can we sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.80,0:35:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说过黑夜狩猎者的案子吗  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you familiar with the Night Stalker case, Delroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听说过  袭击老妇人的家伙  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, the bloke attacking old ladies? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.28,0:35:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻上说你们逮捕了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Said on the news you arrested someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.01,0:36:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.32,0:36:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾地通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm very sorry to tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.09,0:36:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逮捕的人是你父亲  德尔罗伊·伊斯顿·格兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that man is your father, Delroy Easton Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.53,0:36:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  绝对不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No way. It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.97,0:36:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.05,0:36:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有多确认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How sure are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有百分百的确认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we don't have absolute confirmation yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.49,0:36:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果没有极大把握  我们也不会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we wouldn't be here unless we were very sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.97,0:36:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟你父亲多久见一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How often do you see your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.49,0:36:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.05,0:36:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有很长一段时间与他没有来往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For a long time we had nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.16,0:36:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.72,0:36:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我妈  我哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, Mum, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.13,0:36:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.85,0:36:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在我还是小婴儿时弃我们而去  我想是两岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, he walked out when I was a toddler. Two, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.89,0:37:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.45,0:37:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我8还是9岁才再次见到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't see him again till I was eight or nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.45,0:37:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天突然出现在学校门外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turned up at the school gates one day
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.93,0:37:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应要周末带我和我哥去游泳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and promised to take me and my brother swimming at the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.89,0:37:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不太乐意  但她看我们这么期待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mum wasn't keen, but she saw how excited we were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.85,0:37:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就改变了主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and changed her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.28,0:37:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高兴坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was giddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.93,0:37:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像...圣诞节早晨的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like a... kid on Christmas morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.93,0:37:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早就收拾好了的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Had my bags packed hours before
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.51,0:37:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比他预定来接我的时间提前好几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was supposed to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得自己很想向他展示我的后空翻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember I really wanted to show him my backflip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pathetic, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.93,0:37:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他没来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he never turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.04,0:37:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直没再见到他  直到我二十多岁  而且\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't see him again till I was in my 20s and...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.41,0:38:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我已经知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by then I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.93,0:38:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道什么  -他对我妈干的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Knew...? - What he'd done to Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力  殴打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The violence. The beatings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.97,0:38:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让她经历的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What he'd put her through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.89,0:38:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些可怜的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those poor women...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁先联系谁的  你还是你爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who got back in touch, you or your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.53,0:38:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.93,0:38:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me and my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.49,0:38:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告诉我们他再婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone told us that he'd remarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.53,0:38:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妻子有多发性硬化症  说他是个完美的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That his wife had MS and what an amazing husband he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.97,0:38:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个体贴的看护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what an amazing carer...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.05,0:38:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你肯定难以相信吧  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That must've been difficult to believe? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.24,0:38:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着"我得亲眼看看"  所以我们去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"This I have to see," I thought. So we go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"好啊  爸  好久不见"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Hello, Dad. Long time, no see."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.61,0:38:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妻子人很好  但她需要很多照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His wife was sweet, but she needed a lot of care...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.72,0:38:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他在那  细心地照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there he was, providing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.97,0:39:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体贴  耐心  井井有条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kind, patient, everything organised.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.61,0:39:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不嫉妒她  我怎么能呢  但我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't begrudge her, how could I? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着很难受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要告诉你些其他事  德尔罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something else we need to tell you, Delroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完全不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're giving it no credit whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.89,0:39:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你父亲称是你犯下了那些罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but your father has accused you of committing these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.45,0:39:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What...? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.49,0:39:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像帕特丽夏说的  我们完全不信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As Patricia said, we don't believe it for a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们必须通过DNA测试排除你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, er, we will have to eliminate you with a DNA test.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.65,0:39:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等等  他说.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry, hang on, he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.89,0:39:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强奸和那一切  他说都是我干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The rapes and everything? He said it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.76,0:39:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么要这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would he say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.85,0:39:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他就是这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because that's the sort of person he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.93,0:39:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且从你刚才告诉我们的来看  他一直是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, from what you're telling us, always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给你  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- There you go. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.32,0:40:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有鳄梨泥  我给你买了火腿芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They didn't have any torn avocado, I got you ham and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.61,0:40:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.53,0:40:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奶奶92岁了依然染发  所剩无几的头发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My nan's 92 and still dyes her hair... what's left of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.97,0:40:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说当你变老后  似乎就失去了身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said when you get old it's like you lose your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们看不见你  只看到一个老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People don't see you, they just see an old person -
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.68,0:40:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白头发  浅色大衣  老花镜  羊群中的一只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}grey hair, fawn coat, bad glasses, a sheep in a flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.24,0:40:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这案子这么久都没破  隐形的受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's why this went on so long. Victims were invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.65,0:40:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但我们其他人却不承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and the rest of us are in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.37,0:40:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都认为不会发生在自己身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all think it won't happen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.76,0:40:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能逆势而行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll buck the trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便盆  假牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bedpans, false teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.80,0:40:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痴呆  助行架  不可能  不必了  我们不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dementia, Zimmer frame. No way, no thanks. Not us, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.93,0:40:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们助长谎言的方式是忽略他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the way we feed that lie is to ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.65,0:40:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们注意到他们  但却视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, we notice them, but we don't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会避开视线  但也绝不会多看一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't avert our gaze, but we certainly don't linger
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.57,0:41:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们是我们不想要却逃不过的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cos they're the future we don't want and can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.24,0:41:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就像我们在责备他们一般  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's like we blame them, innit.
