Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.93,0:41:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明了我们是怎么样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what the fuck does that say about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.72,0:41:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ok?
