Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其他人相比  有47.5的10的24次方倍几率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"is 47.5 septillion times more likely to be linked to the DNA
