Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.80,0:42:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们在搜查到DNA的两个现场看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As they're present at two of the scenes where we got DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.32,0:42:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他没有DNA的现场也有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and loads of scenes where we didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.89,0:42:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将他与其他数起案件联系在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it links him to literally dozens of offences.
