Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.57,0:42:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.41,0:42:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰特先生  你被起诉犯下22起罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr Grant, you are charged with 22 offences
