Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.93,0:42:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和11起盗窃罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 11 burglaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:42:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管你拒绝认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Notwithstanding that you deny them,
