Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.80,0:43:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔伯恩的督察已经退休后继续工作五年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DI up in Kilburn got his bus pass five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.41,0:43:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-五年  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Five years? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.93,0:43:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前两天还破了一桩双杀案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Closed a double murder the other day.
