Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.28,0:44:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.24,0:44:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接受了我  当其他人都不怎么情愿的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You let me in when, er, the others weren't so inclined.
